## 2. How [app_intent_chat.py](file:///Users/ishanthahewaratne/Documents/Reserch%20New/Branitz2/src/branitz_heat_decision/ui/app_intent_chat.py) Drives the System

You are using [app_intent_chat.py](file:///Users/ishanthahewaratne/Documents/Reserch%20New/Branitz2/src/branitz_heat_decision/ui/app_intent_chat.py) as the main interface. Here is the **exact data flow** from your chat input to the visualizations:

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph UI["Streamlit Split-Panel UI (app_intent_chat.py)"]
        direction TB
        LP["LEFT PANEL\nChat + AI Orb"]
        RP["RIGHT PANEL\nVisualizations"]
    end

    LP -->|"user_input"| PM["_process_message()"]
    PM -->|"route_request(query, cluster_id, context)"| ORCH["BranitzOrchestrator\n(agents/orchestrator.py)"]

    ORCH -->|"1. classify_intent(query)"| NLU["IntentClassifier\n(nlu/intent_classifier.py)\nGemini LLM + keyword fallback"]
    NLU -->|"intent + entities + confidence"| ORCH

    ORCH -->|"2. conversation.resolve_references()"| CONV["ConversationManager\n(agents/conversation.py)\nFollow-up detection, metric switching"]
    CONV -->|"enriched intent"| ORCH

    ORCH -->|"3. guardrail.validate_request()"| GUARD["CapabilityGuardrail\n(agents/fallback.py)\nBlocks unsupported operations"]
    GUARD -->|"can_handle?"| ORCH

    ORCH -->|"4. executor.execute(intent, street_id)"| EXEC["DynamicExecutor\n(agents/executor.py)\nHead Chef"]

    EXEC -->|"_create_agent_plan()"| PLAN["Agent Plan\ne.g. [cha, dha, economics]"]
    PLAN --> EXEC

    EXEC -->|"sequential execution"| DA["Domain Agents\n(agents/domain_agents.py)"]

    subgraph DA_SUB["Domain Agents (Layer 2)"]
        CHA_A["CHAAgent"]
        DHA_A["DHAAgent"]
        ECON_A["EconomicsAgent"]
        DEC_A["DecisionAgent"]
        UHDC_A["UHDCAgent"]
        WIF_A["WhatIfAgent"]
    end

    DA --> DA_SUB

    subgraph ADK["ADK Tools (Layer 1) — subprocess.run()"]
        T1["run_cha_tool"]
        T2["run_dha_tool"]
        T3["run_economics_tool"]
        T4["run_decision_tool"]
        T5["run_uhdc_tool"]
    end

    CHA_A --> T1
    DHA_A --> T2
    ECON_A --> T3
    DEC_A --> T4
    UHDC_A --> T5

    subgraph SCRIPTS["Core Scripts (the muscles)"]
        S1["01_run_cha.py\npandapipes hydraulics"]
        S2["02_run_dha.py\npandapower load flow"]
        S3["03_run_economics.py\nLCOH + Monte Carlo"]
        S4["cli/decision.py\nDeterministic rules"]
        S5["cli/uhdc.py\nJinja2 HTML report"]
    end

    T1 --> S1
    T2 --> S2
    T3 --> S3
    T4 --> S4
    T5 --> S5

    S1 & S2 & S3 & S4 & S5 -->|"write JSON/HTML"| RES[("results/\ncha/ dha/ economics/\ndecision/ uhdc/")]

    RES -->|"read back"| DA_SUB
    DA_SUB -->|"AgentResult"| EXEC
    EXEC -->|"_integrate_results()"| ORCH
    ORCH -->|"_format_answer() + _create_viz()"| RESP["response dict\n{answer, type, data, sources,\nexecution_plan, agent_trace}"]

    RESP --> PM
    PM -->|"append to messages"| LP
    PM -->|"data + type"| RP

    subgraph VIZ["Right-Panel Renderers"]
        V1["_render_co2()\nAltair bar chart"]
        V2["_render_lcoh()\nAltair bar chart"]
        V3["_render_violations()\nMetric cards"]
        V4["_render_network_design()\niframe map"]
        V5["_render_what_if()\nBaseline vs Scenario"]
        V6["_render_fallback_ui()\nCapability list"]
    end

    RP --> VIZ
```

### Step-by-step when you type a question

1. **You type** in `st.chat_input()` (left panel, line 762)
2. **Street extraction** — if no street selected, NLU's [extract_street_entities()](file:///Users/ishanthahewaratne/Documents/Reserch%20New/Branitz2/src/branitz_heat_decision/nlu/intent_classifier.py#298-383) tries to find one in your query (line 773)
3. **[_process_message()](file:///Users/ishanthahewaratne/Documents/Reserch%20New/Branitz2/src/branitz_heat_decision/ui/app_intent_chat.py#650-683)** (line 650) calls `orch.route_request(user_input, cluster_id, context)`
4. **Orchestrator** classifies intent via Gemini → resolves follow-ups via [ConversationManager](file:///Users/ishanthahewaratne/Documents/Reserch%20New/Branitz2/src/branitz_heat_decision/agents/conversation.py#70-405) → checks guardrails → dispatches to [DynamicExecutor](file:///Users/ishanthahewaratne/Documents/Reserch%20New/Branitz2/src/branitz_heat_decision/agents/executor.py#50-408)
5. **Executor** builds an agent plan (e.g. `["cha", "dha", "economics"]` for LCOH) → runs each domain agent in order
6. **Domain agents** check cache → if miss, delegate to ADK tool → which runs the CLI script as a subprocess
7. **Scripts** do the heavy physics (pandapipes/pandapower/NumPy) → write results to [results/](file:///Users/ishanthahewaratne/Documents/Reserch%20New/Branitz2/src/branitz_heat_decision/agents/orchestrator.py#105-109)
8. **Results flow back** through agents → executor → orchestrator formats answer + viz hints
9. **Response stored** in `st.session_state.intent_chat_messages`
10. **Right panel** renders the matching visualization ([_render_co2](file:///Users/ishanthahewaratne/Documents/Reserch%20New/Branitz2/src/branitz_heat_decision/ui/app_intent_chat.py#363-386), [_render_lcoh](file:///Users/ishanthahewaratne/Documents/Reserch%20New/Branitz2/src/branitz_heat_decision/ui/app_intent_chat.py#388-411), etc.)

